	<div class="title">
		<h1 class="posttitle"><a href='http://btcgeek.com/how-to-get-free-litecoins/' class='entry-title' rel='bookmark' title='Litecoin Faucets: How to Get Free Litecoins (LTC)' >Litecoin Faucets: How to Get Free Litecoins (LTC)</a></h1>
		<div class="postdata fix">
					<span class="category"><span class="icon">&nbsp;</span><a href="http://btcgeek.com/category/alternate-cryptocurrencies/" title="View all posts in Alternate Cryptocurrencies" rel="category tag">Alternate Cryptocurrencies</a>, <a href="http://btcgeek.com/category/litecoin/" title="View all posts in Litecoin" rel="category tag">Litecoin</a></span>
